text: Guillermo Eduardo Díaz Zambrano (29 December 1930 – 25 September 1997) was a Chilean football midfielder. He played for Chile in the 1950 FIFA World Cup. He made nineteen appearances from 1950 until 1957.1950 FIFA World Cup Brazil ==References== Category:1930 births Category:1997 deaths Category:Chilean footballers
